# Traffic Light Controller

## Overview
Finite State Machine (FSM) based traffic light controller.

## Board
Arty A7 (Artix-7)

## Tools
- Verilog
- Xilinx Vivado

## Description
Implements a traffic signal system with defined states and transitions for red, yellow, and green lights.

## Inputs
- Clock
- Reset

## Outputs
- LEDs representing traffic signals

## Notes
Demonstrates FSM design and timing-based state transitions.
